          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">T<hi rend="small-caps">HE</hi> greatest monarch may be stabb'd by night,</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-2" n="2">And fortune help the murd'rer in his flight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-3" n="3">The vilest Ruffian may commit a rape,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-4" n="4">Yet safe from injured innocence escape:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-5" n="5">And calumny, by working under ground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-6" n="6">Can, unreveng'd, the greatest merit wound.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-7" n="7"><lb/>What's to be done? shall wit and learning chuse</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-8" n="8">To live obscure, and have no fame to lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-9" n="9">By censure frighted out of honour's road,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-10" n="10">Nor dare to use the gifts by heav'n bestow'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-11" n="11">Or fearless enter in thro' virtue's gate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-CWJS-line-12" n="12">And buy distinction at the dearest rate.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
